##
##  DESCRIPTION
##      Set a new system host name
##
##  USAGE
##      SetHostName <NewName>
##
##          <NewName>           New host name for this system
##
##  EXAMPLE
##      SetHostName Brontes     # Change system name to "Brontes"
##
##  NOTES
##      REQUIRES ROOT ACCESS! REQUIRES FIGLET!
